OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStorm Dave
OL,6,Fwill bring strong winds this evening
OL,7,Fwith some heavy and blustery spells of
OL,8,Frain at times. The storm will clear in
OL,9,Fthe early hours and winds will ease.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FSunny spells and scattered
OL,12,Fshowers on Easter Day with lighter
OL,13,Fwinds. Mostly dry by the afternoon but
OL,14,Ffeeling colder than previous days with
OL,15,Fa fresh breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
